e state govt. has also announced to start various other schemes as given below."}, "003-section": {"000-title": "YSR Navaratnalu \u2013 Other Schemes", "001-normal": "Andhra Pradesh YSRCP govt. headed by CM Jagan has also started various other schemes for people recently which are as follows:-  \n \u2014 [YSR Rythu Bharosa Scheme](https://sarkariyojana.com/ysr-rythu-bharosa-scheme-andhra-pradesh/) \u2013 This scheme for farmers in AP would launch on 15 October 2019. All the farmers to get Rs. 12,500 per annum under this investment support scheme.  \n \u2014 [YSR Arogyasri Scheme](https://sarkariyojana.com/andhra-pradesh-ysr-aarogyasri-scheme/) \u2013 Universal Health coverage to all lower and middle class families whose annual income is less than Rs. 5 lakh. All the expenses above Rs. 1,000 to be borne by the AP state govt.  \n \u2014 [YSR Pension Kanuka Scheme](https://sarkariyojana.com/ysr-pension-kanuka-scheme-andhra-pradesh/) \u2013 Old Age Pension (OAP), Widow, Weavers, Toddy Tappers, Fishermen, Single women, PLHIV (Art pensions), traditional cobblers pension amount raised to Rs. 2250. Disability pension is now Rs. 3,000. CKDU / Dialysis pension raised to Rs. 10,000 and the age of old age pensioners is reduced from 65 to 60 years.", "002-normal": "Source / Reference Link: https://www.ysrcongress.com/top-stories/cm-ys-jagan-promises-rs-15000-68130"}}